neverDiscloseInfo: Never disclose your private key. Anyone with that key has access to your funds. Ensure it is stored securely.
gasInfo: A gas token can’t be switched off, as you do need to pay for transactions with it.
transakContent: Transak lets you buy crypto with your credit card or via bank transfer depending on location. To cover fees (gas) or interact with dApps you’ll mostly need the gas token (the first token of the account).
onRamperContent: Onramper is an aggregated service providing the best quote from several sources and accepts popular payment methods depending on location.
feeAndLimit: Fees and limits may vary. It usually takes just a couple of minutes and requires registration.
weRecommedToStart: We recommend to start with sending ETH to your Liquality wallet because that fuels many transactions. Or you can also buy crypto at our trusted partners.
